Write a Java program that performs addition, subtraction, multiplication and division based on the user input (you can use java.util.
Scanner class to take input). The program takes the value of both the numbers (entered by user) and then user is asked to enter the 
operation (+, -, * and /), based on the input program performs the selected operation on the entered numbers using switch case.

NOTE: Do it creating a class

Write a Java Program that calculates the factorial of a number. Input can be taken from user.
